 Verification

 1. Start a session, say "my name is Alice" → fact should appear in buffer (not MEMIT)
 2. /status → shows "Buffer: 1/20"
 3. Say "Actually, remember my real name is Bob" → surprise fires → buffer consolidates
 4. Check ledger → facts now persisted
 5. Kill process mid-conversation with buffered facts → restart → buffered facts gone, previously consolidated facts intact
 6. /sleep → pre-sleep flush empties buffer before audit begins
